{
  "stem": "26576.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And at the age of two, he had got poliomyelitis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I really think about those times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You know, we were not allowed to see him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It's unbelievable how Australia looked, how Melbourne was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Now, when you talk about it, people-- people don't believe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I'll tell you what happened, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- Yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did it happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well John used to get-- he used to get tonsillitis, the same way as I used to get them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And once, he got a tonsillitis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because I couldn't speak English, I took a doctor that wasn't qualified, but spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she came, and she said, he's got tonsillitis, and nothing to worry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then, I suddenly realized that he can't swallow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I desperately rung to tell her that he can't swallow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The moment she heard that, she didn't want to come, because she obviously realized the he must be sick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somebody said to me, just take a normal doctor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we couldn't even speak to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But finally, we did take somebody, which was very nice, and immediately realized that there was something seriously wrong.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he took us-- he took us with the child to the children's hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But what was terrible that I didn't-- the moment I realized-- the moment I [INAUDIBLE] test, and I realized that it's poliomyelitis, they put him to Fairfield, and you couldn't see him.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I went six weeks without being able to contact him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Each time I would ring, they would tell me either he's reasonable or he's not so good, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I didn't know what it means even.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Look, it was such a horrible thing that I asked friends to ring for me, and I thought maybe I don't understand.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
